11 pages, including 2 figures. Revised version: corrected typos;
  improved presentation; some additional discussion; new appendix with main
  formulae. To appear in J. Phys.: Condens. Matter

To appear in: Proceedings of the International Congress of
  Differential Geometry in the memory of A. Gray, held in Bilbao, Sept. 2000;
  Contemp. Math., AMS 2001
